name: BBQ Ranch Chicken Salad
description: Taste big flavor that truly stands alone with fire-roasted corn, Applewood Smoked Bacon, warm grilled chicken, diced tomatoes and Marzetti® Simply Dressed® BBQ Ranch Dressing.

name: Pepperoni Pizza
description: Our Original Crust topped with Traditional Red Sauce, Whole-Milk Mozzarella and Premium Pepperoni.

name: Spicy Chicken Sandwich
description: A boneless breast of chicken seasoned with a spicy blend of peppers, hand-breaded, pressure cooked in 100% refined peanut oil and served on a toasted, buttered bun with dill pickle chips. Also available on a Golden Wheat Bun.

name: Chicken Quesadillas
description: A grilled flour tortilla stuffed with Cajun-seasoned grilled chicken, pico de gallo and a blend of cheeses.

name: 10 Kentucky Nuggets
description: Our signature Kentucky Nuggets are made with 100% breast chicken, coated in the secret recipes of 11 herbs and spices, and cooked until golden brown. Includes BBQ Dipping Sauce.

name: Hummus Trio
description: You'll love our hummus! Try three varieties: basil pesto, red pepper and classic hummus. Served with pita bread, olives, and cucumbers.
